parameters.name: QUALITY_FLAG
parameters.description: Quality indicator (also quickly shows times when images are available)

parameters.name: IMAGE_DATA
parameters.description: Far UV Images (kRay), small format display with click-expand (~10 min res)

parameters.name: IMAGE_DATA_LF
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Large format display with click-expand, no geographic registration

parameters.name: GEOD_IMAGE_O
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) With geographic map overlay

parameters.name: GEOD_IMAGE_PS
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Azimuthal projection to geographic (with fixed sun orientation)

parameters.name: GEOD_IMAGE_M
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Azimuthal projection to magnetic LT and invariant lat, using eccentric dipole model

parameters.name: IMAGE_MOVIE
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Movie display of images, no geographic registration

parameters.name: IMAGE_MOVIE_O
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Movie, with geographic map overlay

parameters.name: IMAGE_MOVIE_PS
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPANS) Movie, azimuthal projection to geographic (with fixed sun orientation)

parameters.name: IMAGE_MOVIE_M
parameters.description: --> (USE SHORT TIME SPAN) Movie, azimuthal projection to magnetic LT and invariant lat, using eccentric dipole model

parameters.name: GCI_LOOK_DIR
parameters.description: Unit vector along field of view.

parameters.name: DSP_ANGLE
parameters.description: Offset angle of despun platform from nadir.
